hite\">招标人：盐城市第一人民医院</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-align:right;background:white;word-break:break-all\" align=\"right\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;background:white\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;background:white\">时间：<span>2021</span>年<span>8</span>月<span>12</span>日<span>&nbsp; </span></span></p>','','','','','');
INSERT INTO `p8_cms_item_article_addon` VALUES ('2231','3053','1','','','1、盐城市第一人民医院北区9、10号楼消火栓地埋管道更换项目，资金已落实，招标人盐城市第一人民医院现对该项目进行公开招标，诚邀潜在的投标人参加投标。2、项目概况与招标内容2.1项目名称：盐城市第一人民医院北区9、10号楼消火栓地埋管道更换项目。2.2项目地点：盐城','192.168.162.110','192.168.162.110','1628734271','<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:24.0pt;\r\nbackground:white\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;\r\nbackground:white\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;background:\r\nwhite\">、盐城市第一人民医院北区<span>9</span>、<span>10</span>号楼消火栓地埋管道更换项目，资金已落实，招标人盐城市第一人民医院现对该项目进行公开招标，诚邀潜在的投标人参加投标。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:24.0pt;\r\nbackground:white\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;\r\nbackground:white\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;background:\r\nwhite\">、项目概况与招标内容</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:24.0pt;\r\nbackground:white\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;\r\nbackground:white\">2.1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;background:\r\nwhite\">项目名称：盐城市第一人民医院北区<span>9</span>、<span>10</span>号楼消火栓地埋管道更换项目。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:24.0pt;\r\nbackground:white\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;\r\nbackground:white\">2.2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;background:\r\nwhite\">项目地点：盐城市第一人民医院北区</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white\">（毓龙西路<span>166</span>号）</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:24.0pt;\r\nbackground:white\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;\r\nbackground:white\">2.3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;background:\r\nwhite\">招标内容：盐城市第一人民医院北区<span>9</span>、<span>10</span>号楼消火栓室外地埋管道更换为架空管道，室内消火栓管道安装连接等。具体内容详见招标人提供的工程量清单。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:24.0pt;\r\nbackground:white\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;\r\nbackground:white\">2.4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;background:\r\nwhite\">发包方式：包工包料。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:24.0pt;\r\nbackground:white\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;\r\nbackground:white\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;background:\r\nwhite\">、投标人资格要求</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:24.0pt;\r\nbackground:white\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;\r\nbackground:white\">3.1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;background:\r\nwhite\">投标人须是具有建设主管部门核发的消防设施工程专业承包二级及以上资质的独立法人，并具有有效的安全生产许可证；</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:24.0pt;\r\nbackground:white\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;\r\nbackground:white\">3.2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;background:\r\nwhite\">项目负责人须同时具有机电工程专业二级及以上注册建造师资格证书和有效的安全生产考核合格证（<span>B</span>类）。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:24.0pt;\r\nbackground:white\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;\r\nbackground:white\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;background:\r\nwhite\">、投标报名及招标文件的获取</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:24.0pt;\r\nbackground:white\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;background:white\">请符合上述资质条件的投标人携带单位介绍信（或授权委托书，须注明联系人、电话及邮箱）原件到江苏仁禾中衡工程咨询房地产估价有限公司造价二部（盐城市青年西路<span>8</span>号<span>8</span>楼<span>805</span>室）投标报名，投标报名时间<span>2021</span>年<span>8</span>月<span>12</span>日<span>8</span>时至<span>2021</span>年<span>8</span>月<span>17</span>日<span>18</span>时。联系人：刘永杰，<span>0515-69057406</span>；手机：<span>13626222271</span>。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:24.0pt;\r\nbackground:white\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;\r\nbackground:white\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;background:\r\nwhite\">、本项目评标办法采用“合理低价法”。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:24.0pt;\r\nbackground:white\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;\r\nbackground:white\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;background:\r\nwhite\">、投标申请人有违反《盐城市市场廉政准则规定（试行）》中规定情形的，招标人将拒绝投标报名。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:24.0pt;\r\nbackground:white\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;\r\nbackground:white\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;background:\r\nwhite\">、招投标监督管理机构及投诉电话：盐城市第一人民医院纪检监察室，联系电话<span>0515-66696810</span>。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:24.0pt;\r\nbackground:white\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;background:white\">其余内容详见招标文件。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-align:right;background:white\" align=\"right\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;background:white\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;background:white\">招标人：盐城市第一人民医院</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-align:right;background:white;word-break:break-all\" align=\"right\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;background:white\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;background:white\">时间：<span>2021</span>年<span>8</span>月<span>12</span>日<span>&nbsp; </span></span></p>','','','','','');
INSERT INTO `p8_cms_item_article_addon` VALUES ('2232','3054','1','','/ewebeditor/sysimage/icon16/doc.gif','各医疗设备生产企业、经营企业：根据新冠肺炎疫情防控需要，盐城市第一人民医紧急采购一批高流量湿化治疗仪，项目资金已落实，将于近期开展市场调研和招标。欢迎符合条件的医疗设备生产企业、经营企业前来参与。设备名称：高流量湿化治疗仪采购数量：20台（其中5台立即','192.168.162.110','192.168.162.110','1628734390','<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:30.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#333333\">各医疗设备生产企业、经营企业：</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:10.0pt;margin-left:0cm;layout-grid-mode:char;font-size:11.0pt;font-family:\'Tahoma\',\'sans-serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:30.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:#333333\">根据新冠肺炎疫情防控需要，盐城市第一人民医紧急采购一批高流量湿化治疗仪，项目资金已落实，将于近期开展市场调研和招标。欢迎符合条件的医疗设备生产企业、经营企业前来参与。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:10.0pt;margin-left:0cm;layout-grid-mode:char;font-size:11.0pt;font-family:\'Tahoma\',\'sans-serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:30.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:#333333\">设备名称：高流量湿化治疗仪</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:10.0pt;margin-left:0cm;layout-grid-mode:char;font-size:11.0pt;font-family:\'Tahoma\',\'sans-serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:30.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:#333333\">采购数量：<span>20</span>台（其中<span>5</span>台立即采购，<span>15</span>台协议供货）</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:30.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#333333\">有意愿参与本次市场调研的医疗设备生